 * Perl provider support.
 *
 * USAGE: pl_calltime.d 	# hit Ctrl-C to end
 *
 * FIELDS:
 *		FILE		Filename of the Perl program
 *		TYPE		Type of call (sub/total)
 *		NAME		Name of call
 *		TOTAL		Total elapsed time for calls (us)
